## 1. Complete Feature List

### User Management
- Optional login for free users (with ads)
-Mandatory login for paid subscribers
-No Ads for paid subscribers
-User registration tied with email
-Password reset

### VPN Connection
- Connect to VPN server  
- Disconnect from VPN server  
- Server selection (3 servers initially)  
- Connection status display  
-Auto-reconnect

### Security & Networking
- Encrypted traffic (WireGuard)  
- User data isolation  
- Secure authentication  
-Traffic routing via VPN servers
-Network essentials: IP assignment, DNS protection, routing

### Revenue & Ads
-Ads for free users
-Paid subscription for ad-free experience

### Optional / Future Enhancements
- Auto-connect on device start  
- Basic analytics or usage logs (for user info only)  

## 2. Feature Prioritization

### Priority 1 – Core Features
- User login / registration  
- Connect / disconnect VPN  
- Server selection  
- WireGuard encryption
-Paid subscriber login (ad-free experience)
-Free user optional login (with ads)
- Connection status  

### Priority 2 – Important Features
- User logout  
- Password reset  
- Data privacy & isolation  

### Priority 3 – Optional Features
- Auto-connect  
- Basic usage analytics  
